(HY000): Region is unavailable\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"3e3ae9b1-83c4-441d-b8ab-837309e6d19f\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"GET\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"317ef832-9072-447b-a2ff-a8505237d063\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-18T19:10:47.964015836Z\"\"}\",出现次数:13\naiops-k8s-04,frontend,frontend-0,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\\\"\"OLJCESPC7Z\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"2a8d57f0-4223-45af-bd0c-b697c5ca550d\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"317ef832-9072-447b-a2ff-a8505237d063\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-18T19:12:57.985429659Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,frontend,frontend-2,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to get product recommendations: failed to get recommended product info (#L9ECAV7KIM): rpc error: code = Unknown desc = Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"07d12e47-2cc9-4d27-8e4b-92316af85471\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"GET\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"ca2fbeb9-7095-4f9b-bc7e-4f628926ada4\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-18T19:21:33.30175497Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-01,frontend,frontend-1,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"could not retrieve product: rpc error: code = Unknown desc = Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"6700f817-2ae3-4232-96e3-ae733039e759\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"a1174572-90a0-4162-bf9d-f1cccce8cb34\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-18T19:22:32.2136402Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["productcatalogservice-2", "frontend-2", "frontend-0", "frontend-1", "productcatalogservice-0", "productcatalogservice-1"], "service_name": ["productcatalogservice", "frontend"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-01", "aiops-k8s-08", "aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-06"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault occurred from 2025-06-18T19:10:04Z to 2025-06-18T19:29:04Z. Please identify the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-18 19:10:04+00:00 to 2025-06-18 19:29:04+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "从取得的日志数据中，我们可以看到明显的故障模式，许多服务都抱怨一个共同的问题，即 `Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable`。这种错误主要影响了 `productcatalogservice` 和 `frontend` 服务。根据日志数据，我们可以分析如下：\n\n### 关键错误模式\n- **错误类型**: `Region is unavailable`\n- **日志标签**: `productcatalogservice--Error 9005`, `frontend--Error 9005`\n- **异常名称**: `HY000`\n- **错误关键词**: `rpc error: code = Unknown`, `request error`\n\n### 检测的日志关键词\n- `Region is unavailable`\n\n### 设置 Component 与 Reason\n- **组件**: `tidb-tikv or tidb-pd` 因为区域不可用问题是TiDB存储层特有的，`productcatalogservice`和`frontend`都报告此问题，这表明问题起源于存储层。\n- **原因**: `Region is unavailable导致服务性能问题`\n\n### 验证结论\n根据收集到的日志和现有的假设，经过分析我们可以得出结论支持之前的假设：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"Region is unavailable\", \"rpc error: code = Unknown\", \"Error 9005\", \"HY000\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tikv or tidb-pd\",\n      \"reason\": \"Region is unavailable导致服务性能问题\",\n      \"evidence\": \"产品目录服务和前端服务均报错Error 9005: Region is unavailable，表明存储层故障是根因。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n通过上述信息，我们可以初步确认存储层（TiDB存储层）出现Region不可用的问题导致了服务性能问题，进一步验证需要查看TiDB配置和状态来确认问题所在。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于获取的异常指标数据，我将进行详细的分析以确认假设的有效性，即 'TiDB storage layer (tidb-tikv or tidb-pd) is responsible for the region unavailability causing subsequent service performance issues.'。\n\n### 异常指标分析\n\n**异常指标**:\n\n- **TiDB 相关指标**:\n  - `duration_99th` 在 `tidb-tidb` 显著增加，从 0.01 到 64.88 (99th 百分位变化率非常高)，表示查询执行时间急增。\n  - `store_unhealth_count` 在 `tidb-pd` 从 0.0 增加到 1.0，表示存储层健康状态出现异常。\n  - `failed_query_ops` 的异常变动，表明查询故障增多。\n\n- **服务端指标**:\n  - `productcatalogservice` `rrt` 从 7250.37 显著增加到 20164885.29，存在高延迟。\n  - `productcatalogservice` 产生了高 `error_ratio`，达到 52.74。\n  - 其他多个服务例如 `cartservice`, `shippingservice` 也有显著的 `client_error_ratio` 上升，显示链式反应。\n\n### 归因分析\n\n根据指标，TiDB 存储层的 `duration_99th` 和 `store_unhealth_count` 是故障的核心，因为该指标的显著变化与所有受影响服务的高延迟和错误率相匹配。考虑到 TiDB 是数据存储的核心组件，存储层出现问题将导致所有依赖于它的服务出现连锁故障。这与 `productcatalogservice` 等服务的异常表现完全吻合。\n\n### JSON 输出\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"duration_99th\",\n    \"store_unhealth_count\",\n    \"failed_query_ops\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tidb\",\n      \"reason\": \"Abnormal duration_99th indicates excessive query duration possibly due to storage layer issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"duration_99th spiked from 0.01 to 64.88.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-pd\",\n      \"reason\": \"store_unhealth_count increase indicates TiDB storage layer health issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Store unhealth count rose from 0.0 to 1.0.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**总结**: 数据支持TiDB存储层的异常作为故障的根因，导致服务性能的连锁问题。", "trace_analysis_findings": "通过对异常期间的调用链数据分析，我们可以提取以下关键信息：\n\n### 延迟分析\n\n在 `hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct` 操作上，我们观察到以下延迟倍数：\n\n- `frontend-2` 调用 `productcatalogservice-1` 的延迟倍数约为 4087.60 倍（正常: 9681ms, 异常: 39550671ms）\n- `frontend-0` 调用 `productcatalogservice-2` 的延迟倍数约为 3912.41 倍（正常: 10040ms, 异常: 39307039ms）\n\n这些结果显示 `ProductCatalogService/GetProduct` 的请求在异常期间显著增加了延迟，且异常请求次数多达 38 次及以上。\n\n### 错误状态\n\n在 `hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct` 操作中，`Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable` 错误反复出现：\n- `frontend-0` 到 `productcatalogservice-2` 多次返回 `Error 9005` 共 93 次。\n- `frontend-2` 到 `productcatalogservice-1` 返回了 71 次。\n\n这些信息表明 `productcatalogservice` 在接口调用时遇到了区域不可用的频繁错误，该错误与 TiDB 存储层的区域不可用状态一致。\n\n### 鉴于以上分析结果\n\n根据分析数据，《TiDB storage层》成为主要嫌疑，因为我们在产品目录服务上看到了显著的响应时间倍增以及反复的 TiDB 特有错误 `Error 9005`。结合调用链的拓扑分析，这些错误和延迟指向了 TiDB 的问题导致了上游服务的异常。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"frontend-2->productcatalogservice-1\", \"frontend-0->productcatalogservice-2\", \"error_ratio\", \"Error 9005\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"TiDB storage layer\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ProductCatalogService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Significant delay during anomaly period\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n这样的分析得出了 TiDB 存储层异常是区域不可用的主要原因，从而影响了上游 `productcatalogservice` 运行。"}
